name: baking with spatula mixing bowl and scooping to tray
short_script: The subject scoops mixture with the right hand using the spatula. The subject transfers the mixture with the right hand to tray. The subject scrape cleans the spatula with the right hand.

name: carry organizer with both hands at chest height
short_script: The subject carries draw organizer tray and walks forward. The subject turns body towards right side of body to face the opposite direction and walks forward. The subject turns back around and walks in new direction.

name: carry side table with both hands walk around
short_script: The subject carries the side table and walks forward. The subject walks towards right side of body in an arch shape path to face the opposite direction. The subject carries the side table and walks in new direction.

name: carry vase right hand transfer to left hand transfer to right hand walk around
short_script: The subject carry vase with right hand transfer to left hand walk back and forth repeatedly.

name: carry wok turner right hand walk around
short_script: The subject carry wok turner with right hand walk back and forth repeatedly.

name: carrying cutting board with right hand
short_script: The subject carries cutting board with right hand. The subject walks back and forth.

name: carrying whisk with right hand
short_script: The subject carries whisk with right hand. The subject walks back and forth.

name: checking floor lamp with right hand
short_script: The subject check floor lamp with right hand.

name: checking organizer medium on table
short_script: The subject picks organizer medium from table, checks it and puts it back on the table.

name: chopping and slitting with knife
short_script: The subject chops the vegetables on cutting board. The subject slits the vegetables on chopping board.

name: cleaning cutting board with soap
short_script: The subject cleans both sides of the cutting board with soapy sponge in sink.

name: cleaning knife with soap dispenser
short_script: The subject cleans knife in sink with soap dispenser

name: dispensing soap on left hand and washing
short_script: The subject press soap dispenser with right hand to dispense soap on left hand. The subject rubs hands together. The subject washes hands under an imaginary water tap.

name: drag floor lamp walk back
short_script: The subject drags floor lamp while walking back and forth.

name: drag side table walk around
short_script: The subject drags the side table with right hand. The subject walks back and forth.

name: dragging turning  clothes rack walking on ground
short_script: The subject drags clothes rack on ground.

name: drinking from mug with right hand
short_script: The subject moves the mug towards head. The subject drinks from the mug.

name: drinking from mug1 and talking
short_script: The subject looks towards right side of body and moves both hands in different directions. The subject grasps the vacuum flask and tilts the vacuum flask towards mug#2 and mug#1. The subject drinks from mug#1.

name: dropping blanket and blouse from clothes rack to woven basket on left
short_script: The subject grasps and drops the blanket from the clothes rack to the woven basket. The subject grasps and drops the blouse from clothes rack to the woven basket.

name: eating from plastic bowl with spoon
short_script: The subject is sitting behind the table. The subject eats food with spoon from plastic bowl.

name: examining cutting board
short_script: The subject lifts the cutting board. The subject examines the cutting board.

name: flipping pancake in frying pan with turner
short_script: The subject stirs turner in frying pan. The subject flicks the pancake in frying pan.

name: getting off bed and touch table lamp then grasp clothes from clothes rack
short_script: The subject straighten back. The subject stretch both hands. The subject turn right and put both feet on ground. The subject turns off the table lamp and stands up. The subject walks to the clothes rack. The subject grasps clothes hanger#1 and clothes hanger#2.

name: grasp and touch notebook with right hand from side table
short_script: The subject grasps the notebook from the side table. The subject touches notebook with right hand. The subject puts the notebook down on the side table.

name: grasp and transfer woven basket from top shelf to ground while stretch
short_script: The subject grasps woven basket with both hands. The subject transfers woven basket with both hands from shelf to ground.

name: lift shelf lie to stand
short_script: The subject pull shelf with both hands from lie to stand.

name: lifting and checking basket 90
short_script: The subject lifts basket 90. The subject checks the weight of basket 90 with right hand. The subject checks the texture of basket 90 with left hand.

name: lifting and lowering utility cart with both hands
short_script: The subject grasps and lifts the utility cart with both hands. The subject lowers and puts utility cart with both hands down.

name: lifting and putting down dining chair
short_script: The subject lifts the dining chair with both hands. The subject holds the dining chair with both hands above the ground. The subject puts down the dining chair with both hands on the ground.

name: lifting and tilting table
short_script: The subject lifts one side of table off ground. The subject tilts the table 90 degrees. The subject places the table on the ground.

name: lifting dining chair from backrest and placing back with right hand on ground
short_script: The subject lifts the dining chair with right hand. The subject moves the dining chair with right hand from right side to front. The subject gently places the dining chair with right hand on the ground.

name: lifting floor lamp and placing down
short_script: The subject lifts the floor lamp with right hand. The subject moves the floor lamp with right to right side. The subject places the floor lamp with right hand on the ground.

name: lifting frying pan and transfering eggs to side plate with shaky hands
short_script: The subject lifts the heavy frying pan with hands. The subject transfers egges inside frying pan to side plate with both hands.

name: lifting side table and putting down
short_script: The subject lifts the side table with both hands off the ground. The subject puts side table down on ground.

name: lifting working chair and putting back
short_script: The subject lifts the working chair with left hand. The subject holds the working chair with both hands. The subject puts back the working chair with both hands on the ground.

name: move clothes rack with both hands
short_script: The subject drags the clothes rack with right hand towards body. The subject pushes the clothes rack with both hands further from body.

name: moving low chair with both hands
short_script: The subject picks low chair up with both hands and walks forward. The subject puts low chair on the ground and picks it up again. The subject turns to opposite direction and walks forward.

name: organizing and transfering utensils to draw organizer tray
short_script: The subject organizes and transfers cooking utensils to draw organizer tray.

name: peel mango with peeler by rotating mango in left hand from left
short_script: The subject grasps the peeler with right hand. The subject grasps the mango with left hand. The subject peels the mango with both hands.

name: pick up fallen chair and place on ground
short_script: The subject pickes up the fallen chair from the ground. The subject place the chair on the ground.

name: picking wash tub and trash can in woven basket
short_script: The subject picks wash tub from ground, places it in trash can, then places the trash can in the woven basket.

name: placing phone laptop on table replacing table lamp mug picking up notebook
short_script: The subject arranges items on table in office.

name: placing trash can down and leaving trash in trash can
short_script: The subject places trash can with both hands on ground. The subject picks trash from ground. The subject drops trash in trash can.

name: plugging usb in back of laptop with right hand
short_script: The subject plugs the USB into the rear port of laptop with right hand.

name: pour from vaccum flask to mug and drink
short_script: The subject pours from the vaccum flask to mug. The subject drinks from the mug.

name: pour from vacuum flask and peel and cut mango
short_script: The subject pours from vacuum flask. The subject peels mango with peeler. The subject cuts mango with knife.

name: pouring liquid from mug into trash can
short_script: The subject picks up mug from table. The subject pours liquid from mug into trash can. The subject places mug on table.

name: pull low chair from back and front and walk backward
short_script: The subject grasps the low low chair from back and walk. The subject grasps the seat of the low chair and pulls it back.

name: pulling and pushing the dining chair from back post
short_script: The subject pulls the dining chair towards the subject. The subject moves the dining chair away from the subject.

name: reading notebook under table lamp on low chair in left side of side table
short_script: The subject turns table lamp on. The subject picks notebook up.The subject sits on low chair.

name: rearranging the gradvis vase from bottom shelf to top shelf
short_script: The subject bends over. The subject picks up vase.The subject stands up.

name: roll soap dispenser head
short_script: The subject roll soap dispenser head with both hands.

name: sit on dining chair and drink from mug and shake mug
short_script: The subject sits on the dining chair. The subject drinks from mug.

name: sitting on working chair at table working with laptop drinking coffee with mug in left hand
short_script: The subject brings lunch at table. The subject sits on working chair. The subject eats lunch.

name: step on step stool and transfer woven basket from top shelf to ground
short_script: The subject stands on step stool. The subject transfers woven basket with both hands from shelf to ground.

name: subject leaning against metalic clothes rack sliding right then left
short_script: The subject leans against the top bar of the clothes rack. The subject slides the clothes rack to the right. The subject slides the clothes rack to the left.

name: sweeping and flipping blouse on hanger with lint roller on table from left to right
short_script: The subject grasp the lint roller. The subject grasp and sweeps the blouse with lint roller.

name: taking off clothes and hanging on rack
short_script: The subject takes of their clothes. The subject hangs the clothes on clothes rack.

name: transfer deep plate side plate and serving bowl to table with both hands
short_script: The subject transfers deep plate from right hand to the table. The subject transfers side plate from left hand to the table. The subject transfers serving bowl from between both hands to the table.

name: transfer from woven basket to wash tub
short_script: The subject puts clothes from woven basket into wash tub.

name: transfer mango and plastic bowl from side table and basket
short_script: The subject takes a basket from the left side of the side table with left hand. The subject transfers the mango and plastic bowl to the side table from the basket. The subject returns the mango and the plastic bowl to the basket with right hand.

name: transfer mug and side plate from side table to utility cart and return
short_script: The subject transfer mug from side table to utility cart. The subject transfer side plate from side table to utility cart. The subject transfer mug from utility cart to side table. The subject transfer side plate from utility cart to side table.

name: transfer spoon knife and plastic bowl from basket to the table
short_script: The subject grasps the plastic bowl from the basket and moves it to the table. The subject grasps knife from the basket and moves it to the table. The subject grasps the spoon from the basket and moves it to the table.

name: transfer vase from utility cart to shelf then to utility cart with both hands
short_script: The subject grasps and transfers the vase from utility cart to shelf. The subject grasps and transfers vase from shelf to utility cart.

name: turning working chair right with right foot three times
short_script: The subject looks down. The subject bends back a little. The subject moves the working chair with right foot right.

name: walk with low chair
short_script: The subject lifts low chair with right hand. The subject carries low chair. The subject walks back and forth.

name: walking back and forth while pushing the clothes rack with right hand then left hand
short_script: The subject is holding the clothes rack with right hand and walks to the right side of the room. The subject grasps the clothes rack center with left hand and walks to the left side of the room.

name: walking back and forth with the draw organizer tray in right hand while raising then switching hands
short_script: The subject is holding draw organizer tray with right hand. The subject walks to the right side of the room then raises the draw organizer tray. The subject walks to the left side of the room and switches hands.

name: washing clothes with right hand in wash tub
short_script: The subject holds wash tub under water tap. The subject places wash tub on the ground and scrubs clothes inside it.

name: working with laptop and drinking coffee with right hand
short_script: The subject types on laptop. The subject drinks from the mug with both hands.
